    <item>
      <title>Version 3.0.1</title>
      <sparkle:version>17</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.0.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>What's New in VoiceFlow 3.0</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>VoiceFlow AI &amp; Cloud subscriptions — zero-config managed AI and cloud transcription, no API keys needed</li>
          <li>8 AI enhancement presets per profile — Clean &amp; Correct, Professional, Bullet Points, Summary, Key Takeaways, Q&amp;A, Action Items</li>
          <li>Microphone selection — choose your input device in Engine settings</li>
          <li>Dictation statistics — track words spoken, time saved, sessions, and AI usage</li>
          <li>Automatic transcription cleanup — strips noise artifacts from all engines</li>
          <li>Faster update checks every 12 hours</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
